latestIgtvVideos.title: Skin treatment ft Sakhiya skin clinic
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A few days back I could feel that my skin was quite unhealthy. Tiredness, uneven skin tone, and scary acne marks, everything was clearly visible on my skin and I couldn’t really take that stress. So, I decided to visit a dermatologist at Sakhiya Skin Clinic and after the detailed examination, they suggested Passion Peptide Peel treatment for my skin. 
This treatment is blended with natural fruit extracts & medical effectiveness. It rejuvenates your skin and balances out the moisture and skin tone, also treats acne, blemishes & aging spots. It has no side effects & results are quite effective & rapid. 
And honestly, it did wonders on my skin. Right after the treatment, I could feel that my skin was bright & glowing.

Highly recommended for someone who is facing all such skin problems as I did. For any skin concerns do visit @sakhiyaskinclinic for the best treatments and consultants.
#dhruvishajariwala #sakhiyaskinclinic #skintreatment
